    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "EG",
    "text": "This is my family. On my right, my husband, Stefan. We've been married these 49 and 1/2 years. There's not far to go for our golden. Behind me is my oldest daughter, Kay. And next to her, her husband, Joe Ronec At the very back, my one and only son, Greg. The curly hair here, is my youngest daughter, Margaret. And next to her, I'm sorry, I almost left you behind, Greg's wife, Cindy. Next to me, my cousin, Yanke. She came as a great surprise to visit me on my 70th birthday, and I'm very happy to have her here on this day. And in front, my grandchildren-- Jana, who is 16, and Daniel, 14. I hope they will all look at this tape one day and see what happened to their Babush during the war, and never, ever allow anything like that to happen to them or their children or their grandchildren. You tell, Kay.",
